title.narrative: Himachal Pradesh Mid-Himalayan Watershed Development Project

description.narrative: The primary objective of the proposed project is to reverse the process of degradation of the natural resource base and improve the productive potential of natural resources and incomes of the rural households in the project areas. The secondary objective is to support policy and institutional development to harmonize watershed development projects and policies across the State in accordance with best practices.
